<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_157_r2l7">Elſpethen <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>veſtemb<ex>er</ex>g</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_157_r2l8">geſeʒʒen cʒü Tünnfelt / . </ab>
</div>
