<ab facs="#facs_157_r2l10"><expan>Jung<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>Burg<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> / Mit dem <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>vvege<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_157_r2l11">geredt / . 
<del rend="strikethrough">vnd </del> Alſo / daʒ er ſprichet / Sey es / daʒ Jr Jm <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_157_r2l12"><expan>ſeine<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>Scheimbot<ex>e</ex>n</expan> mit <expan>ſeine<ex>m</ex></expan> gewalt / frewntlıchs <expan>recht<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"> ſeit </del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_157_r2l13">
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>hiecʒwiſch<ex>e</ex>n</expan></del> cʒü Slüʒʒelfelt / ſeit / <expan>hiecʒwiſch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_157_r2l14">frawen tag cʒü 
<del rend="strikethrough">N </del> Liechtmeʒʒ nu ſchirſt / . Das wölle er <expan>neme<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
