</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_157" id="77r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Elspethen <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>Vestemb<ex>er</ex>g</expan>, gesezzen czü Tünnfelt</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Liebe fraw, als ir uns <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habt
                                <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>Hanse<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>Ryet<ex>er</ex>s</expan> dez <expan>jung<ex>e</ex>n</expan>,
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex>s</expan>, <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan>, mit dem
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> geredt, also daz er sprichet, sey es daz ir im
                                <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>seine<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>scheimbot<ex>e</ex>n</expan> mit <expan>seine<ex>m</ex></expan>
                        gewalt frewntlichs <expan>recht<ex>e</ex>n</expan> czü Slüzzelfelt seit
                                <expan>hieczwisch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und<app><note><q type="date">
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan> frawen tag czü liechtmezz nu schirst</q>02.02.1409</note></app>. Das
                        wölle er <expan>neme<ex>n</ex></expan> und sein klag auf dem lantgericht die
                        weil besteen lassen. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut
                            <expan>sup<ex>ra</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
